OL,4,CSt Paul's Cathedral could close without
OL,5,Ctourism cash
OL,6, St Paul's Cathedral may have to close
OL,7, permanently if more regular funding is
OL,8, not found, bosses have warned.
OL,10,FThe world-famous London landmark relies
OL,11,Falmost entirely on tourist income from
OL,12,Fticket sales and has seen its finances
OL,13,Fdevastated by the pandemic.
OL,15,FThe building's income dropped by 90% in
OL,16,F2020 as it remained shut. There has
OL,17,Fbeen a similar fall so far this year.
OL,19,FDean of St Paul's, the Very Rev Dr
OL,20,FDavid Ison, said "big decisions" were
OL,21,Fneeded for the historic building.
